author: @a1hiroller
text:
[TRANSLATION] 131230 {#IU} “Season’s Greetings” from #아이유

"Hello, I’m IU. It’s time to wrap up 2013, I filmed two dramas this year and released a full-length album after a long while too. I even released a repackaged album and had a concert. It’s been a really frantic and busy year. I’m not sure about you guys but I hope you’ll stay strong and enjoy what’s left of this year. 2014 is the year of the green horse, so I hope all of you will be lively like the green horse too. You’ve worked hard this year, so all the best for next year. This is IU."

translated by squishy, with love

author: @a1hiroller
text:
[TRANSLATION] 131230 {#IU} “Season’s Greetings” from #아이유

Hello, I’m IU. It’s time to wrap up 2013, I filmed two dramas this year and released a full-length album after a long while too. I even released a repackaged album and had a concert. It’s been a really frantic and busy year. I’m not sure about you guys but I hope you’ll stay strong and enjoy what’s left of this year. 2014 is the year of the green horse, so I hope all of you will be lively like the green horse too. You’ve worked hard this year, so all the best for next year. This is IU.

Translated by squishy with love
